Clubcard voucher distribution announcement

It’s time to thank our loyal customers. We will be distributing the clubcard vouchers to eligible customers starting this Wednesday 4th Shrawan. 

What is BBSM clubcard Voucher? 
BBSM registered clubcard members can collect points every time they make a purchase from our stores. After collecting the points, members can redeem these points to get a cash voucher which can be spent at any of our stores. 

Members eligible for the voucher will receive an sms or a call from us and your points will have been deducted from your app. 

Thank you for shopping with us again.

Thai flavors in the Himalayas & Bhat-Bhateni Thai Fair 🇹🇭🏔️
A vibrant celebration of Thai culture unfolded across Bhat-Bhateni stores in Naxal, Maharajgunj, and Patan — jointly organized with the Royal Thai Embassy.
The event was graced by Hon. Foreign Minister Dr. Arzu Rana Deuba, His Excellency Mr. Suwapong Sirisorn, and other distinguished ambassadors.
With Thai food demos, vendor stalls, a lighting ceremony, and ribbon cutting, the fair was a colorful success filled with flavor, friendship, and festivity! 🎊🍜
